OL,3,CInside the new 1,500-place prison
OL,4,Cwhere inmates can learn trades
OL,6,FA new prison which can house about
OL,7,F1,500 inmates has opened in East
OL,8,FYorkshire as the government tries to
OL,9,Ftackle overcrowding.
OL,11,FCategory C HMP Millsike, which is the
OL,12,Fsize of 39 football pitches, is the
OL,13,Flatest step towards ministers' target
OL,14,Fto create 14,000 extra prison places
OL,15,Fby 2031.
OL,17,FThe jail has been designed to cut
OL,18,Freoffending, with 24 workshops and
OL,19,Ftraining facilities aimed at getting
OL,20,Fprisoners into work after they are
OL,21,Freleased.
