OL,3,CInside the new 1,500-place prison
OL,4,Cwhere inmates can learn trades
OL,6,FMillsike will receive its first
OL,7,Fprisoners at the end of April.
OL,9,FOpening the prison, Justice Secretary
OL,10,FShabana Mahmood was shown around the
OL,11,Ffacility and re-enacted the use of
OL,12,Fpolice cells to hold prisoners.
OL,14,FShe said prisons were operating at
OL,15,Fmore than 99% occupancy, despite
OL,16,Fthousands of prisoners being freed
OL,17,Fearly in a bid to ease overcrowding
OL,18,Fsince September last year.
