OL,3,CInside the new 1,500-place prison
OL,4,Cwhere inmates can learn trades
OL,6,FMs Mahmood said the system was on the
OL,7,F"brink of collapse" nine months ago
OL,8,Fand faced running out of space
OL,9,Fentirely within weeks.
OL,11,FShe said: "Had we not acted, the
OL,12,Fresult would have been catastrophic.
OL,13,FOur courts would have ground to a halt
OL,14,Fand the police would have been forced
OL,15,Fto stop arrests.
OL,17,F"We would have faced a total breakdown
OL,18,Fof law and order."
