OL,3,CInside the new 1,500-place prison
OL,4,Cwhere inmates can learn trades
OL,6,FMs Mahmood said HMP Millsike "sets the
OL,7,Fstandard for the future because it is
OL,8,Fa prison designed to cut crime".
OL,10,FAs well as the cell blocks, she was
OL,11,Fshown workshops which will enable 500
OL,12,Foffenders at a time to train in skills
OL,13,Fsuch as cleaning, bricklaying,
OL,14,Fbarbering and carpentry.
OL,16,FShe said: "We must be honest about the
OL,17,Fchallenges we face.
OL,19,F"While this new prison is necessary we
OL,20,Fsimply cannot build our way out of the
OL,21,Fprisons capacity crisis.
