OL,3,CInside the new 1,500-place prison
OL,4,Cwhere inmates can learn trades
OL,6,FHMP Millsike, which has been built
OL,7,Fnext to the existing Category A Full
OL,8,FSutton Prison has been fitted with
OL,9,Fstate-of-the art security technology
OL,10,Fto combat drugs, drones and phones.
OL,12,FIt has barless windows, hundreds of
OL,13,FCCTV cameras and X-ray body scanners
OL,14,Fto stop illicit supplies getting into
OL,15,Fprison.
OL,17,FThe prison will be run by contractor
OL,18,FMitie Care and Custody, while
OL,19,Feducation and training will be run by
OL,20,FPeoplePlus.
